column5: OK. I wonder why a guy needs to have a holstered pistol on his belt to make a You Tube video? He must wear it to bed with his hot 10 crazy woman. Tell me something I don't know. In my experience hot 10 crazy women usually end up as old bat cat ladies. The hot factor dives quickly after 45 leaving only the crazy factor.  Sorry I couldn't listen to him for the entire 7 minutes.
